---

<Layout
    title="Marketing Digital y SEO | Devanthos - Estrategias que Generan Impacto"
    description="Potenciamos tu presencia digital con estrategias personalizadas de marketing, gestión de redes sociales y creación de contenido que generan impacto, construyen futuro y crean legado.">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative min-h-screen overflow-hidden px-4 py-20">
        <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-500/20 via-transparent to-rose-400/20">
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -top-40 -right-40 h-80 w-80 rounded-full bg-rose-500/30 blur-3xl">
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-40 -left-40 h-80 w-80 rounded-full bg-red-400/40 blur-3xl">
        </div>

        <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto mt-16">
            <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
                <div class="mb-6 flex justify-center">
                    <Badge variant="outline" className="px-4 py-2 text-xs md:text-lg">
                        <Heart className="mr-2 h-4 w-4 text-red-500" />
                        Generamos Impacto, Construimos Futuro y Creamos Legado
                    </Badge>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-12 text-center">
                    <h1 class="font-cocogoose mb-6 text-2xl leading-tight sm:text-3xl md:text-6xl">
                        Marketing Digital y
                        <span
                            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-rose-500 bg-clip-text text-nowrap text-transparent">
                            Gestión de Redes Sociales
                        </span>
                        <span class="sr-only"
                            >en Argentina - Especialistas en posicionamiento web Google, campañas de
                            pago por clic, gestión de redes sociales Instagram Facebook TikTok y
                            estrategias de conversión digital</span
                        >
                    </h1>

                    <p class="text-muted-foreground mx-auto mb-8 max-w-3xl md:text-xl">
                        Potenciamos tu presencia digital con estrategias personalizadas de
                        marketing, gestión de redes sociales y creación de contenido que <strong
                            >generan impacto, construyen futuro y crean legado</strong
                        >.
                        <span class="sr-only"
                            >Servicios profesionales de SEO técnico on-page y off-page, Google Ads y
                            Facebook Ads optimizadas, content marketing, analítica web con Google
                            Analytics 4, social media management y estrategias de growth hacking
                            para empresas.</span
                        >
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 items-center gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2">
                    <div class="space-y-6">
                        <Alert className="border-red-200 bg-red-50">
                            <Heart className="h-4 w-4 fill-red-600 stroke-red-600" />
                            <AlertTitle className="text-red-800"
                                >En Devanthos tejemos historias digitales</AlertTitle
                            >
                            <AlertDescription className="text-red-700">
                                Somos un equipo apasionado por el marketing digital y la creación de
                                contenido, dedicados a potenciar la presencia en línea de negocios
                                como el tuyo.
                            </AlertDescription>
                        </Alert>

                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row">
                            <Button
                                href="#paquetes"
                                size="lg"
                                class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-rose-500 px-8 text-lg hover:from-red-600 hover:to-rose-600">
                                Ver Paquetes
                                <ArrowRight className="ml-2 h-5 w-5" />
                            </Button>
                            <Button
                                href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=56934248692&text=Hola%2C%20quiero%20una%20consulta%20gratuita%20sobre%20marketing%20digital%20y%20SEO."
                                target="_blank"
                                rel="noreferrer"
                                variant="outline"
                                size="lg"
                                class="border-red-500 px-8 text-lg text-red-600 hover:bg-red-50">
                                Consulta Gratuita
                            </Button>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="relative">
                        <img
                            src="/images/service/marketing-digital-seo.avif"
                            alt="Marketing Digital y SEO"
                            class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl"
                        />
                        <div
                            class="absolute -right-4 -bottom-4 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-rose-500 p-4 text-white shadow-lg">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                                <TrendingUp className="h-6 w-6" />
                                <div>
                                    <p class="font-semibold">+100 Clientes</p>
                                    <p class="text-sm opacity-90">Satisfechos</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What We Do Section -->
    <section class="bg-muted/30 px-4 py-20">
        <div class="container mx-auto">
            <div class="mx-auto mb-16 max-w-4xl text-center">
                <h2 class="font-cocogoose text-2xl leading-tight tracking-tight md:text-6xl">
                    ¿Qué Hacemos?
                    <span class="sr-only"
                        >Agencia de marketing digital especializada en posicionamiento SEO,
                        publicidad digital y gestión de redes sociales</span
                    >
                </h2>
                <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-2 mb-8 md:text-xl">
                    En <strong>Devanthos</strong>, nos especializamos en potenciar el alcance de
                    nuestros clientes a través de servicios integrales de marketing.
                    <span class="sr-only"
                        >Expertos en auditorías SEO, investigación de palabras clave, link building,
                        creación de contenido optimizado, gestión de Google My Business y
                        estrategias omnicanal para maximizar el ROI digital.</span
                    >
                </p>

                <div class="mb-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2">
                    <Badge variant="outline" className="text-sm">Auditorías de Marketing</Badge>
                    <Badge variant="outline" className="text-sm">Campañas Publicitarias</Badge>
                    <Badge variant="outline" className="text-sm">Creación de Páginas Web</Badge>
                    <Badge variant="outline" className="text-sm">Gestión de Redes Sociales</Badge>
                    <Badge variant="outline" className="text-sm">Creación de Contenido</Badge>
                    <Badge variant="outline" className="text-sm">Google My Business</Badge>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Platforms -->
            <div class="mx-auto mb-16 max-w-2xl">
                <h3 class="mb-6 text-center text-xl font-semibold">Plataformas donde Trabajamos</h3>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:grid-cols-4">
                    {
                        platforms.map((platform) => {
                            const IconComponent = platform.icon;
                            return (
                                <Card className="text-center p-4 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                                    <CardContent className="p-0">
                                        <IconComponent className="mx-auto mb-2 size-12" />
                                        <p class="text-sm font-medium">{platform.name}</p>
                                    </CardContent>
                                </Card>
                            );
                        })
                    }
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Benefits -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
                {
                    benefits.map((benefit) => {
                        const IconComponent = benefit.icon;
                        return (
                            <Card className="text-center p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
                                <CardContent className="p-0">
                                    <div
                                        class={`h-16 w-16 bg-gradient-to-br ${benefit.gradient} mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full`}>
                                        <IconComponent className="w-8 h-8 text-white" />
                                    </div>
                                    <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold">{benefit.title}</h3>
                                    <p class="text-muted-foreground">{benefit.description}</p>
                                </CardContent>
                            </Card>
                        );
                    })
                }
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Social Media Packages -->
    <section id="paquetes" class="px-4 py-20">
        <div class="container mx-auto">
            <div class="mx-auto mb-16 max-w-4xl text-center">
                <h2 class="font-cocogoose text-2xl leading-tight tracking-tight md:text-6xl">
                    Gestión de Redes Sociales
                    <span class="sr-only"
                        >profesional para Instagram, Facebook, TikTok y LinkedIn con creación de
                        contenido original, estrategias de engagement y campañas publicitarias
                        segmentadas</span
                    >
                </h2>
                <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-2 md:text-xl">
                    Ofrecemos tres paquetes diseñados para diferentes necesidades y presupuestos.
                    Cada paquete incluye contenido original, estrategias creativas y campañas
                    publicitarias optimizadas.
                    <span class="sr-only"
                        >Con métricas de performance, análisis de audiencia, community management,
                        diseño gráfico profesional, video marketing y automatización de
                        publicaciones para maximizar alcance orgánico y conversiones.</span
                    >
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 lg:grid-cols-3">
                {
                    socialPackages.map((pkg) => {
                        const IconComponent = pkg.icon;
                        return (
                            <Card
                                className={`relative transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-2xl ${pkg.popular ? 'border-primary ring-primary/20 border-2 ring-2' : ''}`}>
                                {pkg.popular && (
                                    <div class="absolute -top-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 transform">
                                        <Badge className="bg-primary text-primary-foreground px-4 py-1">
                                            <Star className="w-4 h-4 mr-1" />
                                            Más Popular
                                        </Badge>
                                    </div>
                                )}

                                <div class={`h-2 bg-gradient-to-r ${pkg.gradient}`} />

                                <CardHeader className="text-center pb-4">
                                    <div
                                        class={`h-16 w-16 bg-gradient-to-br ${pkg.gradient} mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full`}>
                                        <IconComponent className="w-8 h-8 text-white" />
                                    </div>
                                    <CardTitle className="text-2xl">{pkg.name}</CardTitle>
                                    <p class="text-muted-foreground">{pkg.description}</p>
                                    <div class="text-primary mt-4 text-3xl font-bold">
                                        {pkg.price}
                                    </div>
                                    {pkg.highlight && (
                                        <Badge variant="secondary" className="mt-2">
                                            {pkg.highlight}
                                        </Badge>
                                    )}
                                </CardHeader>

                                <CardContent>
                                    <div class="space-y-3">
                                        {pkg.features.map((feature) => (
                                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                                <CheckCircle className="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                                                <span class="text-sm">{feature}</span>
                                            </div>
                                        ))}
                                    </div>

                                    <Button
                                        href={`https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=56934248692&text=Hola%2C%20quiero%20contratar%20el%20${encodeURIComponent(pkg.name)}%20de%20gesti%C3%B3n%20de%20redes%20sociales.`}
                                        target="_blank"
                                        rel="noreferrer"
                                        class={`mt-6 w-full bg-gradient-to-r ${pkg.gradient} hover:opacity-90`}>
                                        Elegir {pkg.name}
                                        <ArrowRight className="ml-2 w-4 h-4" />
                                    </Button>
                                </CardContent>
                            </Card>
                        );
                    })
                }
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Google My Business Section -->
    <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-32 dark:bg-gray-900">
        {/* Gradient border */}
        <div class="relative container mx-auto grid gap-20 px-4 md:gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1.2fr]">
            <div
                class="via-border absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 z-10 h-px bg-linear-to-r from-transparent to-transparent">
            </div>
            {/* Left side - Content */}
            <div class="order-2 space-y-8 lg:order-1 lg:space-y-12">
                <div>
                    <h2
                        class="font-cocogoose text-2xl leading-tight tracking-tight text-balance md:text-6xl">
                        Ficha de Google My Business
                        <span class="sr-only"
                            >y SEO local - optimización de ficha empresarial, gestión de reseñas,
                            posicionamiento en Maps y estrategias de marketing de proximidad</span
                        >
                    </h2>

                    <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-2 font-medium text-balance md:text-xl">
                        Optimiza tu presencia local y atrae más clientes mediante técnicas de SEO
                        local avanzado, optimización de NAP (nombre, dirección, teléfono), gestión
                        de citations, marketing de reputación online y estrategias de visibilidad en
                        búsquedas por ubicación.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-6 text-lg font-medium">Es de un solo pago único de $100 USD.</div>

                {/* Features */}
                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-5">
                    {
                        googleMyBusinessFeatures.map((feature) => {
                            const Icon = feature.icon;
                            return (
                                <div class="flex gap-2.5 lg:gap-5">
                                    <Icon className="mt-1 size-4 shrink-0 lg:size-5" />
                                    <div>
                                        <h2 class="font-semibold">{feature.title}</h2>
                                        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
                                            {feature.description}
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            );
                        })
                    }
                </div>

                <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
                    <Button
                        href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=56934248692&text=Hola%2C%20quiero%20optimizar%20mi%20ficha%20de%20Google%20My%20Business."
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noreferrer"
                        aria-label="Contáctanos para Optimizar mi Ficha">
                        Contáctanos para Optimizar mi Ficha
                        <ArrowRight className="ml-2 size-4" />
                    </Button>
                    <Button
                        href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=56934248692&text=Hola%2C%20quiero%20consultar%20sobre%20la%20matr%C3%ADcula%20en%20el%20Instituto%20de%20Tierras%20Blancas."
                        aria-label="Mas información"
                        variant="outline"
                        class="max-sm:hidden">
                        Mas información
                        <Plus className="size-4" />
                    </Button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div
                class="relative order-1 -mr-4 lg:order-2 lg:-mr-[max(2rem,calc((100vw-80rem)/2+2rem))] lg:translate-x-10">
                <img
                    src="/images/service/marketing-digital-seo-2.avif"
                    alt="Streamline product interface showing marketing digital SEO"
                    class="size-full max-h-[40rem] overflow-hidden rounded-t-xl object-cover"
                />
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Work Process Section -->
    <section class="py-20">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            <div class="flex flex-col">
                <h2
                    class="font-cocogoose max-w-3xl text-2xl leading-tight tracking-tight md:text-6xl">
                    Nuestro Proceso Detallado de Trabajo
                </h2>
                <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-6 max-w-2xl md:text-xl">
                    En <strong>Devanthos</strong>, trabajamos con una metodología probada que
                    garantiza resultados excepcionales
                </p>
            </div>
            <div
                class="border-border bg-card mt-8 flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl border p-4 sm:p-8 lg:p-11">
                <div class="contents items-center justify-between sm:flex">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Proceso de Trabajo</h3>
                    <Button href="#paquetes" size="sm" variant="outline" class="order-last">
                        Ver Paquetes
                        <ArrowRight className="ml-2 h-5 w-5" />
                    </Button>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-3 flex gap-4 sm:flex-col">
                    <div class="relative">
                        <div
                            class="grid h-full w-4 justify-center gap-10 sm:h-4 sm:w-auto sm:grid-cols-4 sm:items-center">
                            <div
                                class="bg-ring absolute inset-0 left-1/2 w-px -translate-x-1/2 sm:inset-auto sm:left-auto sm:h-px sm:w-full sm:-translate-x-0">
                            </div>
                            <span class="bg-ring relative top-3 size-2 rounded-full sm:top-0"
                            ></span>
                            <span class="bg-ring relative top-3 size-2 rounded-full sm:top-0"
                            ></span>
                            <span class="bg-ring relative top-3 size-2 rounded-full sm:top-0"
                            ></span>
                            <span class="bg-ring relative top-3 size-2 rounded-full sm:top-0"
                            ></span>
                        </div>
                        <div
                            class="animate-timeline-reveal absolute inset-0 grid h-full w-4 justify-center gap-10 sm:h-4 sm:w-auto sm:grid-cols-4 sm:items-center">
                            <div
                                class="bg-primary absolute inset-0 left-1/2 w-px -translate-x-1/2 sm:inset-auto sm:left-auto sm:h-px sm:w-full sm:-translate-x-0">
                            </div>
                            <span class="bg-primary relative top-3 size-2 rounded-full sm:top-0"
                            ></span>
                            <span class="bg-primary relative top-3 size-2 rounded-full sm:top-0"
                            ></span>
                            <span class="bg-primary relative top-3 size-2 rounded-full sm:top-0"
                            ></span>
                            <span class="bg-primary relative top-3 size-2 rounded-full sm:top-0"
                            ></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="grid gap-10 sm:grid-cols-4">
                        {
                            workProcess.map((step) => {
                                return (
                                    <div class="flex h-full flex-col justify-between gap-4">
                                        <div class="flex flex-col">
                                            <div class="bg-border border-border flex h-8 w-fit items-center gap-px overflow-hidden rounded-md border text-sm font-medium">
                                                <span class="bg-background grid h-full place-items-center px-2">
                                                    {step.number.toString().padStart(2, '0')}
                                                </span>
                                                <span class="bg-background grid h-full place-items-center px-2">
                                                    {step.title}
                                                </span>
                                            </div>
                                            <h3 class="mt-5 font-medium">{step.title}</h3>
                                            <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-2 text-sm">
                                                {step.description}
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                        <div>
                                            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                                                <Progress
                                                    value={step.progress}
                                                    className="h-1 flex-1"
                                                />
                                                <span class="text-muted-foreground w-8 text-right text-xs">
                                                    {step.porcentage}
                                                </span>
                                            </div>
                                            <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-1 text-xs">
                                                {step.timeframe}
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                );
                            })
                        }
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <style>
            @keyframes timeline-reveal-mobile {
                from {
                    clip-path: inset(0 0 100% 0);
                }
                to {
                    clip-path: inset(0% 0 0 0);
                }
            }

